  <heading>RDFFR (unpredicated)</heading>
  <desc>
    <brief>
      <para>Read the first-fault register</para>
    </brief>
    <authored>
      <para>This instruction reads the first-fault register (<asm-code>FFR</asm-code>) and places the read values in the
destination predicate without predication.</para>
      <para>This instruction is illegal when executed in Streaming SVE mode, unless FEAT_SME_FA64 is implemented and enabled.</para>
    </authored>
    <predicated>False</predicated>
    <sm_policy>SM_0_only</sm_policy>
  </desc>
